cells.data: ## Goal: Predict which parts will fail quality control

### Data: 

The dataset contains an extremely large number of anonymized features. Features are named according to a convention that tells you the production line, thet station on the line, and the feature number.

E.g. 
L3_S36_F3939 => a feature measured on line 3, station 36, and is feature number 3939

#### features
- categorial data
- numerical data 

#### label
- Binary (response=1 or 0)
